# HTML Payment Form Project

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is a simple HTML-based Payment Form that simulates an online checkout process. It is designed to help beginners understand how payment forms are structured in real-world websites.

---

## 📚 What You Will Learn
In this project, you will learn:

- How to design a payment form in HTML
- How to collect user billing information
- How to use different input types for secure data entry
- How to structure checkout forms like real e-commerce websites

---

## 🧪 Features of This Project
- Customer personal information fields
- Billing address section
- Payment method selection (Credit Card, Debit Card, etc.)
- Card details input (Card Number, Expiry Date, CVV)
- Submit/Pay button
- Clean and structured layout

